Bus Registration for 2020-21 School Year
Registration for busing is now available utilizing the link below. Please remember that every year you must login in, click on your child's name and then "Submit Student Transportation Request" along with selecting Transportation and Session. Once that is completed, go back to the top and select "Submit". Busing registration is open until 7/31/20.

https://www.ezrouting.com/beatricene

Please note...after the July 31st date, if students are not registered they will have to wait until a few weeks after school starts and routes are established to reroute new riders. PLEASE SIGN UP NOW!!
